      <h2>Troubleshooting</h2>
      <p>Having trouble running the game? Here are a few things you can do to try and fix the issue. Make sure you have Java 8 installed and running. Uninstall previous versions of Java to avoid any conflicts and get version 8 <a href="http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/jre8-downloads-2133155.html">here</a> for your operating system.</p>

      <p>If you are still having problems, open up the Java Control Panel, go to the Security tab, and set the security level to high or lower. For insurance, also add <em>http://maxrchung.com</em> into the Exception Site List.</p>

      <img src="security.png" />
      <p class="caption">Java Control Panel, Security tab</p>
      <img src="siteException.png" />
      <p class="caption">Adding <em>http://maxrchung.com</em> to the exception list</p>
